{"type": "article", "id": 34044, "title": "黄铜混凝土文具，给你的书桌多一份质感｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-02T23:02:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 34566, "name": "färska"}, {"id": 34567, "name": "misc-ellany"}, {"id": 34571, "name": "The Atelier YUL"}, {"id": 34572, "name": "Dentsu"}, {"id": 34568, "name": "Thomas Missé"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 207, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161102215755eoNRuz1at03TABsP.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Scroll Chair by färska</h3><p>对于在不知不觉间长大的小朋友而言，一款优秀的家具应该既拥有能陪伴他们一起成长的灵活性，又可以很好地融入到居家环境当中。日本品牌 <a href=\"http://www.farska.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">färska</a> 带来的 <a href=\"http://www.farska.com/product/series/scrollchair\" rel=\"nofollow\">Scroll</a> 儿童椅就满足了以上两点：简洁的圆弧形实木框架不怕孩子碰撞，座椅的部分是一张能够灵活调节的防水布料卷轴，不用担心小朋友找不到最合适的坐姿。不过，中间没有竖档，太活泼的小朋友恐怕要看紧点了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181228Zjz5KVGJQ0UEbwCM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181157H53chaqlGV9oEQBn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181155QizvNBDKrhaG2yug.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181155REsPXKSWTM2ZO9nQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181158pcAsZeaLgvlJqWSz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Minerae by Thomas Missé</h3><p>灯具的开关和明暗调控方式同样是设计师们热衷于探索的领域。在荷兰设计周上，埃因霍温设计学院的 <a href=\"http://www.thomasmisse.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thomas Missé</a> 就带来了这套以不同材质间的互动为特点的 Minerae 灯饰系列。和普通灯饰不同的是，Minerae 本身并没有开关，所有互动都通过金属底座上的岩石来完成。灯饰的铝制底座会对石头进行感应，如果要调整亮度的话只要紧贴底座轻轻移动即可。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181249VRrlFXHQ1SxkindN.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181248vOizhQSnDNWIZFy7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.290954\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611021812480KfsypTYmgMDRaWl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.290954\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181249fKBAaXjZRGpFDIlC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.290954\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ORE by misc-ellany</h3><p>如果你也中意黄铜与混凝土这两种材料的组合，不妨来看看新加坡设计工作室 <a href=\"http://misc-ellany.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">misc-ellany</a> 带来的这套极简风文具 ORE。正方体胶带座和圆柱形的小笔筒都由手工打造而成，精简的造型让未经加工的混凝土突出了铜件的存在感和功能。你可以通过<a href=\"http://misc-ellany.com/shop/shop-all/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些文具，售价从 9 到 59 新加坡元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611021813563bXTecBW5oE1rA6I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181356nlSKL3TjzWews4Rb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181356JRk51v3Sj96hAs8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181356Le1ISRv7obKGOuiq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181356o9rGk1fBzLa57lIU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.630807\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102181356InMOeS1dKolFpgJA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.630807\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Leather Carryalls by The Atelier YUL</h3><p>加拿大品牌 <a href=\"https://theatelieryul.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Atelier YUL</a> 的创始人之一是一位建筑师，当她发现市面上没有好看而且足够大的包容纳她工作所需的大型文件时，她决定设计出为创意工作者量身定制的手提包。经过数次方案的调整，The Atelier YUL 最终将包的款式定为四种，样式都很干净利落。旗下的每一件产品都是由蒙特利尔的皮革匠手工制作而成，售价从 45 到 490 加元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102205515ChQfdBXq0xDWsZu1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102205515dWFimcMPJeBlxI4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102205515lIxr9zUts4wVh6Bv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102205516VsghcBzMCuXpGeR3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102205516PHmTu7GLgxQn6rB8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.501667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>A HAND FireEx by Ting Ray Tuinn</h3><p>生活中常见的灭火器都被设计成需要两手才能操作，考虑到有些人在发生紧急情况时只能空出一只手进行灭火，来自台湾的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/iamhr8011\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ting Ray Tuinn</a> 带来了这款造型独特的灭火器 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43612041/A-HAND-FireEx\" rel=\"nofollow\">A HAND FireEx</a>。罐体上方被改成了一个弧线形的把手，让人联想到伞柄的设计。开关被设计在把手的正面，按起来相当方便。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016110220553221McwK8SR3u0YFWL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102205532bqB1l450c9FikeN8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102205532jnd8F2P0saweXkvp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102205532ejUgoT0b1BRNX796.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102205532ldHgntLbCMJOrP71.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Trash bag of Jack-o’-lantern by Dentsu Inc.</h3><p>在今年日本的 <a href=\"http://www.g-mark.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Good Design Award</a> 中，<a href=\"http://www.dentsu.co.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dentsu</a> 公司为刚刚结束的万圣节游行所设计的<a href=\"http://www.g-mark.org/award/describe/44437\" rel=\"nofollow\">南瓜灯垃圾袋</a>获得了社区发展类的特别奖。为了鼓励人们在游行过程中不随地乱丢垃圾，垃圾袋被设计成了南瓜灯的模样，装满后放在街头就成了漂亮的装饰，进一步增添了节日的气息。为了方便之后的回收程序，垃圾袋的背面还列出了三种不同的垃圾类型供人们打勾分类。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102215827Bzi8OXwKpTfSIW0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102215825QuE8nSGkUd0qoJIB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102215825STXwBFq643Ag2YUV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102215829lhasvgkqy12mYZ09.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646699\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}